      <title>焦点：经过数月的谈判，Yandex 易手，俄罗斯罕见妥协</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/after-months-negotiation-rare-russian-compromise-yandex-changes-hands-2024-02-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两年前莫斯科入侵乌克兰之前，俄罗斯在纳斯达克上市的搜索引擎巨头Yandex的市值曾一度达到300亿美元。本周，一个国内投资者财团同意以 52 亿美元收购该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/after-months-negotiation-rare-russian-compromise-yandex-changes-hands-2024-02-09/</guid>
